read() - Method in class br.ufpe.cin.amadeus.io.ParallelSource
Lê um byte a partir do endereço de STATUS da porta paralela The byte read contains 5 valid bits, corresponing to 5 pins of input from the STATUS pins of the parallel port (the STATUS is located at "portBase + 1", e.g. the STATUS address for LPT1 is 0x379).
